<br>
Zeem, for Magicians, Charm seems to be ok, and not overpowered. Reason: We have no defense, so the risk on charm break is huge. We <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>need</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> some backup of some kind (gate/portal beside us) in order to pull this off solo. We also need specific classes of mobs below a certain level, which are not readily available everywhere.<br>
<br>
Enchanters.. it's a different story. Enchanters can last long enough with their runes to pop off a fast stun, root, mez, blur, something similar. They have the defense even as silk wearers to pull this off, as well as simply being able to mez anything they darn well please unlike us.<br>
<br>
To sum up, Mage charm = trinket and toy and fun at times. Enchanter charm = overpowered at high levels in the planes. Not so much so outside. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52886&quot;"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.ninjacorp.com/Rhasin_sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zeem@themagicianstower>Zeem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 546<br> <font color=#333333>(2/7/03 10:17:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1833.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Kinda...</span><hr size=1> Chanter should be better than us to charm, no question about that, they should be able to do it safer too.<br>
<br>
But there are a few things I would like to see fixed.<br>
<br>
